data.description: Don’t miss this Ideal Location for your new home in sought-after Mountain Ridge community, with low HOA fees that include lawn maintenance. Features: 3 Bedrooms - 2 Baths, Spacious Open Floorplan, Large secondary Bedrooms with walk-in closets. Generous sized primary bedroom features dual closets and en suite bathroom. The main level features an abundance of natural light, new flooring, and granite countertop. Fully Fenced Backyard with Patio, Large 2-Car Garage. Friendly Neighbors. Easy Commute to GA 400 Restaurants, Shopping, Outlet Mall, Healthcare Facilities, Sawnee Mountain Hiking Trails and Lake Lanier Parks. Excellent Forsyth County School District and Low Taxes.
